title: American Horror Story: Double Feature | KPCD 666 CAPE RADIO: CHAPTER 1 - Season 10 | FX
author: FX Networks
comment: Finish this sentence: This is a place where...

Interesting things I've picked up from Chapter 1:

AHS intro sounds can be heard during the intro violin music.
Provincetown is a place for artists (Harry, Austin, and Belle Noir) are all artists.
This radio idea is neat. AHS is the drug my body needs year after year…so excited for the premiere !
I’m really digging the tone and world building of this season so far, I’m hoping it stays consistent.
So happy the OGs are back this season ❤️
